name: Portland area Tableau User Group
body:
### Welcome to PDXaTUG's home on GitHub.
This site will provide information, links, and downloads from past and for future meetings.

### You can connect to PDXaTUG via 
* Tableau Communities [Portland](https://community.tableau.com/groups/portland)
* LinkedIn [Group](https://www.linkedin.com/groups/3858800)
* MeetUp [Group](http://www.meetup.com/Portland-Tableau-User-Group/)
* Twitter [PDXaTUG](https://twitter.com/PDXaTUG)
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
